{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\uc1\htmautsp\deff2{\fonttbl{\f0\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}{\f2\fcharset0 Segoe UI;}}{\colortbl\red0\green0\blue0;\red255\green255\blue255;\red255\green0\blue0;}\loch\hich\dbch\pard\plain\ltrpar\itap0{\lang1033\fs18\f2\cf0 \cf0\ql{\f2 {\fs24\cf2\ltrch Sami Khedira }{\ltrch (German pronunciation: [\u712?sa\u720?mi\u720? xe\u712?di\u720?\u641?a\u720?]; born 4 April 1987) is a German professional footballer who plays as a central midfielder for Serie A club Juventus and the Germany national team.}\li0\ri0\sa0\sb0\fi0\ql\par}
